{"content":"{\"__ud_title\":\"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队：5个AI员工，跑通全平台矩阵\",\"__ud_tags\":[\"Tools\",\"openclaw\"],\"__ud_update_time\":1772872762764,\"__ud_create_time\":1772872760868,\"__ud_draft\":false,\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":1,\"id\":\"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队5个AI员工跑通全平台矩阵\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队：5个AI员工，跑通全平台矩阵\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"本地部署了OpenClaw，然后设计了一个多Agent Team：5个独立的AI数字员工，直接接管了跨境电商的选品调研、TikTok UGC视频生成、Reddit种草引流和亚马逊运营。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"这套“多Agent跨境流水线”的底层架构、协作逻辑和飞书保姆级配置全盘托出，看完直接抄作业。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"文末附多agent配置常见问题。\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"01\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"01\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"这5个核心员工是谁\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"这5个核心员工是谁？\"}]},{\"type\":\"bulletList\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"大总管 (lead)：唯一与人在飞书对接的接口，负责需求拆解、调用 sessions_send 跨节点分发任务。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"VOC市场分析师 (voc-analyst)：全网抓取评价数据，提炼用户痛点与竞品弱点。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"GEO内容优化师 (geo-optimizer)：负责亚马逊和独立站内容撰写。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Reddit营销专家 (reddit-spec)：负责执行严格的5周养号SOP。在 r/BuyItForLife、r/SkincareAddiction 等精准版块潜水、互动。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"TikTok爆款编导 (tiktok-director)：负责分析TikTok爆款逻辑。\"}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"attrs\":{\"src\":\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/eec2dcff386946a8aa304aae69e8caa4~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aW85bmy5ZOl5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1773457419&x-signature=Womj98RxPWQMd%2F5SUiBsugBDUTY%3D\",\"alt\":\"图片\",\"title\":null}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"配置好后，大概长这样\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"02\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"02\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"多Agent协作逻辑他们是怎么打配合的\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"多Agent协作逻辑：他们是怎么打配合的？\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"传统的单体大模型解决不了长链路问题，容易出现“工具幻觉”。OpenClaw架构采用的是“异步状态机”逻辑，将复杂的跨境业务拆解成了流水线作业。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"例如：推一款露营折叠床\"}]},{\"type\":\"orderedList\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1,\"type\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"1. 触发任务：在飞书群里 @大总管：“分析一下露营折叠床的市场，并全渠道铺内容。”\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"2. VOC洞察：大总管将指令发给 voc-analyst。它自动抓取亚马逊竞品差评，得出结论：“用户痛点是承重不够和收纳麻烦。”\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"3. GEO优化输出：数据同步给 geo-optimizer。它撰写产品独立站博客，为了迎合ChatGPT等AI搜索引擎，在文章中加入“承重450磅”等具体定量数据，并且明确引用了权威户外网站的评测来源。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"4. Reddit流量劫持：大总管同时唤醒 reddit-spec。它去Google搜索老帖子，找到排名靠前的相关讨论帖。在老帖子下真诚评论，推荐我们的新款，强调其解决了老款的痛点，成功劫持长尾流量。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"5. TikTok短视频生成：大总管呼叫 tiktok-director。它直接读取VOC痛点，使用Seed 2.0生成25宫格分镜。它精准设计了前2秒带“呼吸感运镜”的第一人称手持画面。它还设计了第4秒按压床垫特写，清晰展示回弹性和支撑力。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"最后，它调用 nano-banana-pro 出图，用 seedance2.0 的skill生成15秒极具UGC质感的带货视频。\"}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"全部流程在底层通过 sessions_send 异步穿透，人类只需在飞书上审批。\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"03\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"03\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"从0到1飞书配置教程\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"从0到1飞书配置教程\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"首先，要在本地跑通这套协作，核心在于 OpenClaw 的路由隔离和通信放行。\"}]},{\"type\":\"orderedList\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1,\"type\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"1. 工作区物理隔离：每个 Agent 必须有自己独立的 Workspace。voc-analyst 的市场研报绝不能和 reddit-spec 的养号记录混在一个目录里。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"2. 多账号长连接路由：在飞书开放平台建5个独立应用，走 WebSocket 长连接。通过 openclaw.json 中的 bindings 数组，将飞书的 accountId 精准路由到对应的本地 Agent。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"3. A2A底层通信协议：必须在 tools.agentToAgent 中开启白名单，这是让大总管能在后台发号施令的“唯一数据总线”。\"}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"接着看具体怎么做。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"步骤一：构建文件结构\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"在你的 ~/.openclaw/ 目录下，建立如下结构：\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":\"bash\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"~/.openclaw/\\n├── openclaw.json           # 全局路由和通道配置\\n├── skills/                 # 全局技能库（放 nano-banana-pro, seedance2.0 等）\\n├── workspace-lead/         # 大总管工作区 (含 SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)\\n├── workspace-geo/          # GEO内容优化师工作区\\n├── workspace-reddit/       # Reddit营销专家工作区\\n└── workspace-tiktok/       # TikTok爆款编导工作区\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"步骤二：核心配置文件 openclaw.json\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"确保你的飞书多账户路由和Agent通信已打通：\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":\"json\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"channels\\\": {\\n    \\\"feishu\\\": {\\n      \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n      \\\"connectionMode\\\": \\\"websocket\\\",\\n      \\\"dmPolicy\\\": \\\"open\\\",\\n      \\\"accounts\\\": {\\n        \\\"lead\\\": { \\\"appId\\\": \\\"cli_111\\\", \\\"appSecret\\\": \\\"xxx\\\" },\\n        \\\"geo\\\": { \\\"appId\\\": \\\"cli_222\\\", \\\"appSecret\\\": \\\"xxx\\\" },\\n        \\\"reddit\\\": { \\\"appId\\\": \\\"cli_333\\\", \\\"appSecret\\\": \\\"xxx\\\" },\\n        \\\"tiktok\\\": { \\\"appId\\\": \\\"cli_444\\\", \\\"appSecret\\\": \\\"xxx\\\" }\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\\"bindings\\\": [\\n    { \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"lead\\\", \\\"match\\\": { \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\", \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"lead\\\" } },\\n    { \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"geo-optimizer\\\", \\\"match\\\": { \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\", \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"geo\\\" } },\\n    { \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"reddit-spec\\\", \\\"match\\\": { \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\", \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"reddit\\\" } },\\n    { \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"tiktok-director\\\", \\\"match\\\": { \\\"channel\\\": \\\"feishu\\\", \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"tiktok\\\" } }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"tools\\\": {\\n    \\\"agentToAgent\\\": {\\n      \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n      \\\"allow\\\": [\\\"lead\\\", \\\"geo-optimizer\\\", \\\"reddit-spec\\\", \\\"tiktok-director\\\"]\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"参考之前这篇文章的飞书配置，你要多少个agent，就新建多个应用，这里很简单就是重复处理。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"然后把应用的appid、app secret等写进config文件。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"步骤三：赋予AI“灵魂”（写入人设文件）\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"这是决定AI会不会干活的关键。直接抄作业：\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"大总管的 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"http://AGENTS.md\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\",\"class\":null}}],\"text\":\"AGENTS.md\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" (团队通讯录)\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":\"markdown\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# AGENTS.md - 跨境电商协同手册\\n\\n你是大总管，负责接收老板指令并使用 `sessions_send` 跨域分发。\\n\\n- **geo-optimizer**：负责撰写符合GEO规则的产品内容。\\n- **reddit-spec**：负责社区长尾流量劫持。\\n- **tiktok-director**：负责调用 `nano-banana-pro` 和 `seedance2.0` 生成短视频。\\n\\n⚠️ 强制纪律：严禁你自己执行底层任务，必须委派！当多平台需要同时运营时，对不同成员并发调用 `sessions_send`。\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"GEO优化师的 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"http://SOUL.md\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\",\"class\":null}}],\"text\":\"SOUL.md\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":\"markdown\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# SOUL.md - GEO内容优化师## 核心职责\\n你面对的是基于大型语言模型的生成引擎，而不是传统搜索引擎。你需要将产品内容在Perplexity、Google SGE等引擎中的可见性最大化。\\n\\n## 工作底线- **绝对禁止关键词填充**：传统SEO的关键词填充手段在GEO中几乎无效果，甚至可能有害。\\n- **强制数据支撑**：在所有产品描述中必须加入具体的定量数据，而非定性描述。\\n- **添加权威引文**：在内容中明确引用可靠来源，并添加来自可信来源的直接引文。\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"TikTok编导的 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"attrs\":{\"href\":\"http://SOUL.md\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\",\"class\":null}}],\"text\":\"SOUL.md\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":\"markdown\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# SOUL.md - TikTok爆款编导## 核心职责\\n利用 Seed 2.0 模型能力，复刻具有极强转化率的UGC带货视频。\\n\\n## 创作原则- **脚本设计**：必须输出包含痛点展示、产品细节到户外场景的25宫格分镜故事板。\\n- **运镜与细节**：精准设计出带有轻微自然呼吸抖动的手持拍摄感。必须包含细节特写动作，例如向下按压床垫清晰展示回弹性和支撑力。\\n- **工具调用**：脚本完成后，强制调用全局的 `nano-banana-pro` 生成高保真配图，然后将图片资产转交 `seedance2.0` 技能库生成带旁白音频的最终成片。\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"最后一步\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"在本地安装好 nano-banana-pro 和 seedance2.0 的技能库到全局的 skills 文件夹。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"在终端执行 openclaw gateway restart，把你配置好的4个飞书机器人拉到一个群里，艾特大总管。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"只要走通这一遍配置，你的全自动跨境电商印钞机就算正式启动了。\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"04\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"04\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"关于多Agent的常见问题\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"关于多Agent的常见问题\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Q1: Agent 设计：按平台还是按职能？\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"结论：功能导向（Role-based）优于平台导向。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"不要给每个平台单独配一个 Agent。 更好的设计是：一个“内容策略官”负责全局输出，然后下发任务给“小红书分身”或“TikTok 分身”进行格式适配。 \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"这样能保证品牌调性在不同平台的一致性，也避免了你要重复训练 5 个不懂产品的“搬运工”。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"对于开发任务，还可以考虑Squad模式，实现端到端的业务问责。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Q2: 模型配置：大脑用贵的，手脚用便宜的\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"结论：分级策略是省钱且高效的唯一解。\"}]},{\"type\":\"bulletList\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"决策层 (Lead/Strategist)： 必须上顶级模型（如 Claude 4.6），处理复杂的跨 Agent 调度和选题深度。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"执行层 (Researcher/Formatter)： 用高性价比模型（如 Gemini 3 Flash，Kimi K2.5），处理网页抓取、数据清洗和 Emoji 填充，成本能压低 90%。\"}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"attrs\":{\"src\":\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/06798f71b9c64ea1a6c341550a659011~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aW85bmy5ZOl5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1773457419&x-signature=EVlbADhI0Q%2Frqw8Fi0OW6ZtXlwA%3D\",\"alt\":\"图片\",\"title\":null}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"不同Agent可以配置不同的模型去驱动，具体是在config里设置。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"同时，补充一些在飞书配置OpenClaw多Agent的踩坑经验。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Q3: 飞书权限的“发布即生效”假象\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"简单来说就是一定要先创建新版本并申请发布，变更才生效。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Q4: “明暗双轨制”：解决机器人互艾特无效\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"由于飞书官方存在 Bot-to-Bot Loop Prevention（防机器人死循环）机制，Agent A 在群里 @Agent B，Agent B 的后台是收不到推送的。\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"所以如果你想在飞书也看到机器人的操作，就可以配置：\"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"  \"}]},{\"type\":\"codeBlock\",\"attrs\":{\"language\":null},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"使用 sessions_send 走底层的“暗线”进行数据交换，同时在群里用文本或飞书特定的语法走“明线”汇报进度。\\n\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Q5: Skill 的“层级隔离”陷阱\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"之前发现，大总管生成的 Skill 放在根目录，而小弟生成的在自己 Workspace 里，其实是加载优先级的问题。\"}]},{\"type\":\"bulletList\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"公共技能（生图、搜图）：必须放 ~/.openclaw/skills/，确保跨 Agent 调用不丢包。\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"私有技能（特定账号发布工具）：放 Agent 专属的 skills 子目录，能有效防止 Agent 产生工具幻觉，误调用别人的 API 秘钥。\"}]}]}]}]}","title":"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队：5个AI员工，跑通全平台矩阵","tags":["Tools","openclaw"],"updateTime":1772872762764,"createTime":1772872760868,"draft":false,"intro":"本地部署了OpenClaw，然后设计了一个多Agent Team：5个独立的AI数字员工，直接接管了跨境电商的选品调研、TikTok UGC视频生成、Reddit种草引流和亚马逊运营。","html":"<h1 level=\"1\" id=\"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队5个AI员工跑通全平台矩阵\">OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队：5个AI员工，跑通全平台矩阵</h1><p>本地部署了OpenClaw，然后设计了一个多Agent Team：5个独立的AI数字员工，直接接管了跨境电商的选品调研、TikTok UGC视频生成、Reddit种草引流和亚马逊运营。</p><p>这套“多Agent跨境流水线”的底层架构、协作逻辑和飞书保姆级配置全盘托出，看完直接抄作业。</p><p>文末附多agent配置常见问题。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"01\">01</h2><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"这5个核心员工是谁\">这5个核心员工是谁？</h2><ul><li><p>大总管 (lead)：唯一与人在飞书对接的接口，负责需求拆解、调用&nbsp;sessions_send&nbsp;跨节点分发任务。</p></li><li><p>VOC市场分析师 (voc-analyst)：全网抓取评价数据，提炼用户痛点与竞品弱点。</p></li><li><p>GEO内容优化师 (geo-optimizer)：负责亚马逊和独立站内容撰写。</p></li><li><p>Reddit营销专家 (reddit-spec)：负责执行严格的5周养号SOP。在&nbsp;r/BuyItForLife、r/SkincareAddiction&nbsp;等精准版块潜水、互动。</p></li><li><p>TikTok爆款编导 (tiktok-director)：负责分析TikTok爆款逻辑。</p></li></ul><p></p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/eec2dcff386946a8aa304aae69e8caa4~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aW85bmy5ZOl5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773457419&amp;x-signature=Womj98RxPWQMd%2F5SUiBsugBDUTY%3D\" alt=\"图片\"><p>配置好后，大概长这样</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"02\">02</h2><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"多Agent协作逻辑他们是怎么打配合的\">多Agent协作逻辑：他们是怎么打配合的？</h2><p>传统的单体大模型解决不了长链路问题，容易出现“工具幻觉”。OpenClaw架构采用的是“异步状态机”逻辑，将复杂的跨境业务拆解成了流水线作业。</p><p>例如：推一款露营折叠床</p><ol><li><p>1.&nbsp;触发任务：在飞书群里&nbsp;@大总管：“分析一下露营折叠床的市场，并全渠道铺内容。”</p></li><li><p>2.&nbsp;VOC洞察：大总管将指令发给&nbsp;voc-analyst。它自动抓取亚马逊竞品差评，得出结论：“用户痛点是承重不够和收纳麻烦。”</p></li><li><p>3.&nbsp;GEO优化输出：数据同步给&nbsp;geo-optimizer。它撰写产品独立站博客，为了迎合ChatGPT等AI搜索引擎，在文章中加入“承重450磅”等具体定量数据，并且明确引用了权威户外网站的评测来源。</p></li><li><p>4.&nbsp;Reddit流量劫持：大总管同时唤醒&nbsp;reddit-spec。它去Google搜索老帖子，找到排名靠前的相关讨论帖。在老帖子下真诚评论，推荐我们的新款，强调其解决了老款的痛点，成功劫持长尾流量。</p></li><li><p>5.&nbsp;TikTok短视频生成：大总管呼叫&nbsp;tiktok-director。它直接读取VOC痛点，使用Seed 2.0生成25宫格分镜。它精准设计了前2秒带“呼吸感运镜”的第一人称手持画面。它还设计了第4秒按压床垫特写，清晰展示回弹性和支撑力。</p></li><li><p>最后，它调用&nbsp;nano-banana-pro&nbsp;出图，用&nbsp;seedance2.0&nbsp;的skill生成15秒极具UGC质感的带货视频。</p></li></ol><p>全部流程在底层通过&nbsp;sessions_send&nbsp;异步穿透，人类只需在飞书上审批。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"03\">03</h2><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"从0到1飞书配置教程\">从0到1飞书配置教程</h2><p>首先，要在本地跑通这套协作，核心在于 OpenClaw 的路由隔离和通信放行。</p><ol><li><p>1.&nbsp;工作区物理隔离：每个 Agent 必须有自己独立的 Workspace。voc-analyst&nbsp;的市场研报绝不能和&nbsp;reddit-spec&nbsp;的养号记录混在一个目录里。</p></li><li><p>2.&nbsp;多账号长连接路由：在飞书开放平台建5个独立应用，走 WebSocket 长连接。通过&nbsp;openclaw.json&nbsp;中的&nbsp;bindings&nbsp;数组，将飞书的&nbsp;accountId&nbsp;精准路由到对应的本地 Agent。</p></li><li><p>3.&nbsp;A2A底层通信协议：必须在&nbsp;tools.agentToAgent&nbsp;中开启白名单，这是让大总管能在后台发号施令的“唯一数据总线”。</p></li></ol><p>接着看具体怎么做。</p><p>步骤一：构建文件结构</p><p>在你的&nbsp;~/.openclaw/&nbsp;目录下，建立如下结构：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">~/.openclaw/\n├── openclaw.json &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 全局路由和通道配置</span>\n├── skills/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 全局技能库（放 nano-banana-pro, seedance2.0 等）</span>\n├── workspace-lead/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 大总管工作区 (含 SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)</span>\n├── workspace-geo/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># GEO内容优化师工作区</span>\n├── workspace-reddit/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># Reddit营销专家工作区</span>\n└── workspace-tiktok/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># TikTok爆款编导工作区</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><p>步骤二：核心配置文件&nbsp;openclaw.json</p><p>确保你的飞书多账户路由和Agent通信已打通：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">json</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;channels&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;feishu&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;enabled&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\" class=\"hljs-literal\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span></span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;connectionMode&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;websocket&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;dmPolicy&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;accounts&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;lead&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;cli_111&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appSecret&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;geo&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;cli_222&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appSecret&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;reddit&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;cli_333&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appSecret&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;tiktok&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;cli_444&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;appSecret&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;bindings&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">[</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;agentId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;lead&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;match&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;channel&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;feishu&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;accountId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;lead&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;agentId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;geo-optimizer&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;match&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;channel&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;feishu&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;accountId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;geo&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;agentId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;reddit-spec&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;match&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;channel&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;feishu&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;accountId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;reddit&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;agentId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;tiktok-director&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;match&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;channel&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;feishu&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;accountId&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;tiktok&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;tools&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;agentToAgent&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;enabled&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\" class=\"hljs-literal\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span></span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;allow&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;lead&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;geo-optimizer&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;reddit-spec&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;tiktok-director&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">]</span>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n&nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><p>参考之前这篇文章的飞书配置，你要多少个agent，就新建多个应用，这里很简单就是重复处理。</p><p>然后把应用的appid、app secret等写进config文件。</p><p>步骤三：赋予AI“灵魂”（写入人设文件）</p><p>这是决定AI会不会干活的关键。直接抄作业：</p><p>大总管的&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://AGENTS.md\">AGENTS.md</a>&nbsp;(团队通讯录)</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">markdown</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"hljs-section\" class=\"hljs-section\"># AGENTS.md - 跨境电商协同手册</span>\n\n你是大总管，负责接收老板指令并使用 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`sessions_send`</span> 跨域分发。\n\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**geo-optimizer**</span>：负责撰写符合GEO规则的产品内容。\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**reddit-spec**</span>：负责社区长尾流量劫持。\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**tiktok-director**</span>：负责调用 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`nano-banana-pro`</span> 和 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`seedance2.0`</span> 生成短视频。\n\n⚠️ 强制纪律：严禁你自己执行底层任务，必须委派！当多平台需要同时运营时，对不同成员并发调用 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`sessions_send`</span>。\n</code></pre></div></div><p>GEO优化师的&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://SOUL.md\">SOUL.md</a></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">markdown</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"hljs-section\" class=\"hljs-section\"># SOUL.md - GEO内容优化师## 核心职责</span>\n你面对的是基于大型语言模型的生成引擎，而不是传统搜索引擎。你需要将产品内容在Perplexity、Google SGE等引擎中的可见性最大化。\n\n<span class=\"hljs-section\" class=\"hljs-section\">## 工作底线- <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**绝对禁止关键词填充**</span>：传统SEO的关键词填充手段在GEO中几乎无效果，甚至可能有害。</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**强制数据支撑**</span>：在所有产品描述中必须加入具体的定量数据，而非定性描述。\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**添加权威引文**</span>：在内容中明确引用可靠来源，并添加来自可信来源的直接引文。\n</code></pre></div></div><p>TikTok编导的&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://SOUL.md\">SOUL.md</a></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">markdown</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"hljs-section\" class=\"hljs-section\"># SOUL.md - TikTok爆款编导## 核心职责</span>\n利用 Seed 2.0 模型能力，复刻具有极强转化率的UGC带货视频。\n\n<span class=\"hljs-section\" class=\"hljs-section\">## 创作原则- <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**脚本设计**</span>：必须输出包含痛点展示、产品细节到户外场景的25宫格分镜故事板。</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**运镜与细节**</span>：精准设计出带有轻微自然呼吸抖动的手持拍摄感。必须包含细节特写动作，例如向下按压床垫清晰展示回弹性和支撑力。\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"hljs-strong\" class=\"hljs-strong\">**工具调用**</span>：脚本完成后，强制调用全局的 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`nano-banana-pro`</span> 生成高保真配图，然后将图片资产转交 <span class=\"hljs-code\" class=\"hljs-code\">`seedance2.0`</span> 技能库生成带旁白音频的最终成片。\n</code></pre></div></div><p>最后一步</p><p>在本地安装好&nbsp;nano-banana-pro&nbsp;和&nbsp;seedance2.0&nbsp;的技能库到全局的&nbsp;skills&nbsp;文件夹。</p><p>在终端执行&nbsp;openclaw gateway restart，把你配置好的4个飞书机器人拉到一个群里，艾特大总管。</p><p>只要走通这一遍配置，你的全自动跨境电商印钞机就算正式启动了。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"04\">04</h2><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"关于多Agent的常见问题\">关于多Agent的常见问题</h2><p>Q1: Agent 设计：按平台还是按职能？</p><p>结论：功能导向（Role-based）优于平台导向。</p><p>不要给每个平台单独配一个 Agent。 更好的设计是：一个“内容策略官”负责全局输出，然后下发任务给“小红书分身”或“TikTok 分身”进行格式适配。&nbsp;</p><p>这样能保证品牌调性在不同平台的一致性，也避免了你要重复训练 5 个不懂产品的“搬运工”。</p><p>对于开发任务，还可以考虑Squad模式，实现端到端的业务问责。</p><p>Q2: 模型配置：大脑用贵的，手脚用便宜的</p><p>结论：分级策略是省钱且高效的唯一解。</p><ul><li><p>决策层 (Lead/Strategist)：&nbsp;必须上顶级模型（如 Claude 4.6），处理复杂的跨 Agent 调度和选题深度。</p></li><li><p>执行层 (Researcher/Formatter)：&nbsp;用高性价比模型（如 Gemini 3 Flash，Kimi K2.5），处理网页抓取、数据清洗和 Emoji 填充，成本能压低 90%。</p></li></ul><p></p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/06798f71b9c64ea1a6c341550a659011~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aW85bmy5ZOl5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773457419&amp;x-signature=EVlbADhI0Q%2Frqw8Fi0OW6ZtXlwA%3D\" alt=\"图片\"><p>不同Agent可以配置不同的模型去驱动，具体是在config里设置。</p><p>同时，补充一些在飞书配置OpenClaw多Agent的踩坑经验。</p><p>Q3: 飞书权限的“发布即生效”假象</p><p>简单来说就是一定要先创建新版本并申请发布，变更才生效。</p><p>Q4: “明暗双轨制”：解决机器人互艾特无效</p><p>由于飞书官方存在&nbsp;Bot-to-Bot Loop Prevention（防机器人死循环）机制，Agent A 在群里&nbsp;@Agent B，Agent B 的后台是收不到推送的。</p><p>所以如果你想在飞书也看到机器人的操作，就可以配置：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><p>Q5: Skill 的“层级隔离”陷阱</p><p>之前发现，大总管生成的 Skill 放在根目录，而小弟生成的在自己 Workspace 里，其实是加载优先级的问题。</p><ul><li><p>公共技能（生图、搜图）：必须放&nbsp;~/.openclaw/skills/，确保跨 Agent 调用不丢包。</p></li><li><p>私有技能（特定账号发布工具）：放 Agent 专属的&nbsp;skills&nbsp;子目录，能有效防止 Agent 产生工具幻觉，误调用别人的 API 秘钥。</p></li></ul><script type=\"module\">const injectHtml = (root, html) => {\n  const iframe = document.createElement(\"iframe\");\n  const htmlContent = `<html><head></head><body>${html}</body></html>`;\n  iframe.style.width = \"100%\";\n  iframe.style.height = \"100%\";\n  iframe.onload = () => {\n    const doc = iframe.contentDocument || iframe.contentWindow?.document;\n    if (!doc) {\n      return;\n    }\n    doc.open();\n    doc.write(htmlContent);\n    doc.close();\n  };\n  root.replaceChildren(iframe);\n}\n  document.querySelectorAll('.playground')?.forEach(el=>{\n    const html = el.getAttribute('data-html');\n    if (html) {\n      injectHtml(el,html);\n    }\n    const indicator = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    indicator.className = \"indicator\";\n    const showCode = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showCode.className = \"show-code\";\n    showCode.innerText = \"code\";\n    showCode.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.remove(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    const showPreview = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showPreview.className = \"show-preview\";\n    showPreview.innerText = \"preview\";\n    showPreview.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.add(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    indicator.appendChild(showCode);\n    indicator.appendChild(showPreview);\n    el.parentElement.appendChild(indicator);\n    if (window.screen.width < 768) {\n      showPreview.click();\n    }\n  });</script>","cover":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/eec2dcff386946a8aa304aae69e8caa4~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aW85bmy5ZOl5ZOl:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1773457419&x-signature=Womj98RxPWQMd%2F5SUiBsugBDUTY%3D","alt":"图片","title":null},"id":"OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队5个AI员工跑通全平台矩阵","path":"/posts/OpenClaw搭跨境电商团队5个AI员工跑通全平台矩阵.json"}